
           Angular Features
           ----------------
1.component (root-AppComponent)

2.module (root-AppModule)

3.data binding:-

  3.1.one way binding

    3.1.1 from view to component

      3.1.1.1 Event binding (click,mouseover,keypress) -(event)="function call"
      3.1.1.2  Event Binding using $event -(event)="function call ($event)"
           .3 Template referencing variable

    3.1.2 from component to view

       3.1.2.1 String interpolation/interpolation {{expression}}
       3.1.2.2 Property binding -[Binding-target]="Binding-source"

    3.2.two way binding  

      3.2.1 ngModel (formsModel)        


4.Dependency Injection/Inversion of control

5.services=>using data sharing

6.Template driven angular forms

7.Model driven angular forms
    7.1 Reactive forms {ReactiveFormsModule}
        7.1.1 Form Group
        7.1.2 Form Array
        7.1.3 Form control

8.Angular Directives
    8.1 component Directives     
    8.2 Structural Directives
        8.2.1 *ngIf="condition"
        8.2.2 *ngFor
        8.2.3 *ngSwitch
    8.3 Attribute Directives
        8.3.1 Inbuilt Attribute Directives -[ngclass]
        8.3.2 Userdefined Attribute Directives    


 9.Local storage
    9.1 setitem
    9.2 getitem
    9.3 removeitem

 10.Parent Child data sharing  
    10.1 @Input - parent to child data sharing     
    10.2 @Output -child to parent data sharing

11.EventEmitter -create events and emit events 

12.Angular Pipes- converting set of Input format
    syntax : expression | pipOperator [: pipArguments]

13. Angular Animations    


